info.senderName: NWS Duluth (Northeast Minnesota and Northern Wisconsin)
info.headline: Winter Weather Advisory issued March 17 at 10:19PM CDT until March 18 at 5:00AM CDT by NWS Duluth
info.description: ...WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY NOW IN EFFECT UNTIL 5 AM CDT SATURDAY... * WHAT...Snow. Additional snow accumulations of up to one inch. * WHERE...North St. Louis and Central St. Louis Counties. This includes the Tribal Lands of the Bois Forte Band, Lake Vermilion and, Nett Lake areas. * WHEN...Until 5 AM CDT Saturday. * IMPACTS...Plan on slippery road conditions. * ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Blowing snow will reduce visibility overnight.
info.instruction: Slow down and use caution while traveling. The latest road conditions can be obtained by calling 5 1 1. Road conditions can also be found at 511mn.org for Minnesota or 511wi.gov for Wisconsin.
